					Latest Key Developments (Source: Significant Developments)




Snipp Interactive reports revenue for Q1 of $2.5 mln
Tuesday, 30 May 2017 10:48pm EDT 
May 30 (Reuters) - Snipp Interactive Inc :Snipp Interactive reports Q1-2017 financial results.Revenue for Q1 2017 of $2.5 million grew 18% when compared to revenue of $2.1 million for Q1 2016.Gross margins improved 1% from 75% for Q1 2016 to 76% in Q1 2017.On March 31, 2017, bookings backlog rose to over US$5.4 million, a 29% increase, bookings backlog at March 31, 2016 was US$5.2 million. 
			
