Snipp announces non-brokered private placement of up to $4.5 million
Friday, 5 May 2017 10:05am EDT 
May 5 (Reuters) - Snipp Interactive Inc :Snipp announces non-brokered private placement of up to $4.5 million.Snipp Interactive Inc- financing will be comprised of up to 45 million common shares at a market price of CAD $0.10 per share.Snipp Interactive Inc- net proceeds raised through financing will be used for sales & marketing and general working capital purposes. 
			
