Wednesday, 23 Mar 2016 07:05am EDT 
Snipp Interactive, Inc:Has signed a digital loyalty agreement with a single brand within the portfolio of one of the largest alcohol beverages companies in the world.Contract is a US$ 135,000 minimum commitment for a short three-month pilot covering three US states only.Based on the success of the pilot, the program will be extended nationally. 
			
