Snipp Interactive Inc announces US$ 2.5 million global cost savings and integration plan
Tuesday, 1 Mar 2016 07:15am EST 
Snipp Interactive Inc:Announces us$ 2.5 million global cost savings and integration plan.Says cutting workforce by 20 percent.Consolidation of its three engineering teams into one team under the direction of snipp's recently appointed CTO.Cost reductions are result of a strategic redesign of its business following the two acquisitions that Snipp carried out in 2015. 
			
