Company Overview of Snipp Interactive Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Snipp Interactive Inc., a technology company, develops and sells mobile-based promotions solutions and associated campaign services worldwide. It offers software applications combined with traditional purchase-related marketing promotions, such as contests and rebates, which allow advertising agencies, brands, and media to engage and interact with customers. The company provides mobile promotions and contests solution, a turnkey contesting platform that offers a range of mobile-based contests, including sweepstakes, win programs, and tiered and multi-level games; and purchase promotions/receipt processing solution, which allows brands to execute customized purchase-based promotions. In addit...
Snipp Interactive Inc., a technology company, develops and sells mobile-based promotions solutions and associated campaign services worldwide. It offers software applications combined with traditional purchase-related marketing promotions, such as contests and rebates, which allow advertising agencies, brands, and media to engage and interact with customers. The company provides mobile promotions and contests solution, a turnkey contesting platform that offers a range of mobile-based contests, including sweepstakes, win programs, and tiered and multi-level games; and purchase promotions/receipt processing solution, which allows brands to execute customized purchase-based promotions. In addition, it provides loyalty programs solution, a white-label loyalty platform that enables clients to deploy punch-card and points-based loyalty programs with rewards stores attached. Further, the company offers smarter rebate solutions platform that allows end-customers to qualify for rebates through mobile devices and receive rebate checks electronically through a multitude of various options; data analytics solution for brands to understand customers, behaviors, and trends; and a robust digital rewards platform that can be used with other solutions or in standalone programs. Additionally, it operates Customer Loyalty Management product, which is multi-currency and cloud-based platform that offers benefits and rewards management, including an advanced analytics platform for reporting and predicting consumer behavior. The company was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Washington, the District of Columbia.
Detailed Description


1605 Connecticut Avenue NWWashington, DC 20009United StatesFounded in 2007



Phone: 888-997-6477

www.snipp.com







